task.summary: Added base libraries and boilerplate to implement Redux state management. Added Bootstrap UI. Implemented Login/Logout functions.

Implement user profile info loading from backend to application state. Implemented dynamic building of main application menu, based on information in user profile. Implemented hierarchial application state and helper methods to extract properties on different hierarchy levels.
Integrated WAB3 framework skeleton and added Products Category entity to it
Added Role model, container and component.
Modified CRUD operations to be compatible with Spring Framework backend. Added multiple value feature to Select control. Added Checkbox control. Added User model
Implemented relationships management for data models. Implemented transient field management for data models. Implemented correct CRUD for User model. Implemented model and UI for Product Categories.

Added access control rules to models. Modified UI of entity lists and controllers, based on access rules. Implemented Discount, PurchaseUser and Shop models. Fixed form UI component and list of model types.
Added Document type entity, list and item. Added Purchase, PurchaseProduct and DimensionUnit models, components and containers.
Added related fields validation. Refactored UI controls to support embedded to table mode. Changed relation saving to backend functions.
Added PurchaseDiscount model. Implemented Products and Discounts tables in purchase with auto-calculated totals. Refactored relationships management.
Improve UI for purchase (scrollable products table and totals). Fix purchases fix function.

Implemented formatting with identation in Product category dropdowns. Fixed Product categories item screen. Implemented auto scroll to bottom when adding new line to products table on purchase detail view.
